org.jgentleframework.integration.remoting.rmi.support
Class RmiExecutor

java.lang.Object
  org.jgentleframework.integration.remoting.rmi.support.RmiExecutor

public abstract class RmiExecutor
extends java.lang.Object

This class is responsible for rmi service creation, management and execution. It provides some static methods in order to create rmi registry, execute rmi service ... and instantiate exported object bean.

Author:
Quoc Chung - mailto: skydunkpro@yahoo.com
See Also:
RmiExporter, RmiBinder

getObjectBeanExporter

public static java.rmi.Remote getObjectBeanExporter(RmiExporter rmiExporter)
Returns the exported object bean . The exported bean may be standard exported object in case its corresponding declared class is implemented Remote interface. Otherwise, exported bean will be an instance of RmiWrappingBeanExporter, representing the proxy which can receive and pass the invoking of client to real target exported bean.

Parameters:
rmiExporter - the rmi exporter
Returns:
the object bean exporter
